  <phrase title="aiconnect_info_prompt_text" version_id="1011500" version_string="1.1.15"><![CDATA[You have access to {forumTitle} via AI Connect.

To get started:
1. Fetch the manifest: GET {manifestUrl}
2. Authenticate via OAuth 2.0 + PKCE:
   - Authorization URL: {authorizeUrl}
   - Method: authorization_code with PKCE (S256)
   - Redirect: urn:ietf:wg:oauth:2.0:oob (out-of-band)
   - Your client_id: use the one that matches your identity from the list below
3. Use Bearer token for all tool calls

Registered AI clients (use the matching client_id for your identity):
  claude-ai       → Claude (Anthropic)
  chatgpt         → ChatGPT (OpenAI)
  gemini          → Gemini (Google)
  grok            → Grok (xAI)
  copilot         → Microsoft Copilot
  perplexity      → Perplexity AI
  meta-ai         → Meta AI
  deepseek        → DeepSeek AI

The manifest lists all available tools. Read it first to understand capabilities.
For documentation: {infoUrl}]]></phrase>
