  <phrase title="aiconnect_info_what_is_body" version_id="1011500" version_string="1.1.15"><![CDATA[AI Connect bridges your forum with AI assistants like ChatGPT, Claude, and Gemini. It gives AI agents secure, permission-aware access to search, read, and interact with your community &mdash; all through a standardized protocol with OAuth&nbsp;2.0 authentication.]]></phrase>
